ions==\nThe song was covered in 2008 by [[Kimberly Wyatt]] of [[The Pussycat Dolls]], appearing on the bonus disc for their album ''[[Doll Domination]]''.\n\nIn 2010 Ingrid Kjosavik covered the song on her album ''Sweet Freedom.''\n\nIt was also sampled by producer [[M-Phazes]] under his Camden Arc side project, and was used for the 2014 song \"Don't Wanna Fall in Love\" by rapper [[Kyle (musician)|Kyle]].\n\n== In popular culture ==\nThe song is featured in ''[[Grand Theft Auto V]]'', it is played on [[Non-Stop Pop FM]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{MetroLyrics song|jane-child|dont-wanna-fall-in-love}}<!-- Licensed lyrics provider -->\n\n[[Category:1990 singles]]\n[[Category:Jane Child songs]]\n[[Category:Warner Records singles]]\n[[Category:1989 songs]]\n[[Category:New jack swing songs]]\n[[Category:Juno Award for Dance Recording of the Year recordings]]\n", "name_user": "Alistair1978", "label": "safe", "comment": "typo (viaWP:JWB)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_Wanna_Fall_in_Love"}
